Class EntityWorkspaceEventHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.workspace.EntityWorkspaceEventHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WorkspaceHandler

    public class EntityWorkspaceEventHandler
extends Object
implements WorkspaceHandler
    Workspace handler for EntityWorkspaceEvent. This workspace handler fires attached actions when the specified entity and event types are matched.

    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
